  "prompt": "How can I apply for my car to be on Overhaulin'?",
  "response": "To apply for your car to be on Overhaulin', you would typically need to:\n\n1. Visit the official Overhaulin' website or their social media channels\n2. Look for a casting call or application form\n3. Fill out the application with details about:\n- Your car's current condition\n- Why your car deserves to be overhauled\n- Your personal story\n- Photos of the vehicle\n\nHowever, it's worth noting that Overhaulin' is not currently in active production. The show originally ran from 2004-2007 on TLC, then had a revival from 2012-2015 on Velocity. As of now, new episodes are not being produced, so applying would not be possible.\n\nIf the show returns in the future, they would likely announce casting calls through their official channels.",
